ygData.subject: Finally level 10
ygData.msgSnippet: Met up with my first war lord which was enough to make me reconsider my sanity in not grouping... i had help but still would of been nice to have someone heal
ygData.messageBody:
Met up with my first war lord which was enough to
make me reconsider my sanity in not grouping... i had
help but still would of been nice to have someone heal
me up...waiting is such a bore. I found that it's
also foolish to log off for a few minutes when you run
the risk of not getting back in. I still have'nt
found a quest yet but have'nt really been looking hard
...do they pay well?<br><br> Beechwoodgrey Lany's
server tree city
